// AI-UI Renderer
// Recursively renders a JSON UIComponent tree into React elements.
// Looks up each component type in the ai-ui registry and instantiates it with
// the provided props and any nested children.

FUNCTION AIUIRenderer(component, onAction, componentProps) -> JSX      EXPORT
  CALLS: getComponent (registry)
  Looks up the component type in the registry via getComponent.
  Merges componentProps into the component's own props.
  Recursively renders each child via AIUIRenderer.
  IF component type is unknown, renders a fallback error badge.
